INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (50, 1, '2014-02-13 17:02:32', '2014-02-13 17:02:32', '[et_pb_section inner_shadow="off" parallax="off"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_cta admin_label="Call Now" title="Call Now for Immediate Service!" background_color="#ab1f2d" use_background_color="on" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="center"]</p><h1> </h1><h1 style="text-align: center;">(310) 555-1212</h1><p>[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="2_3"][et_pb_text admin_label="Text" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]</p><h1>Why choose us</h1><p><a href="http://dev1.ken-shoufer.com/fixall/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/van3trimmed1.png"><img class="size-medium wp-image-334 alignleft" src="http://dev1.ken-shoufer.com/fixall/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/van3trimmed1-300x135.png" alt="van3(trimmed)" width="300" height="135" /></a>There are many plumbing companies in California and there are more than a dozen servicing the entire Los Angeles County. How do you choose a plumbing company in Paramount and surrounding areas in California? Do you have a list of criteria based on which you can assess the positive attributes and shortcomings of plumbers in your area? Any decision has to be based on factual information and FixAll Plumbing gives you more than half a dozen reasons that would more than rationalize why you should choose our services.</p><p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="2_3"][et_pb_text admin_label="solilguy slider" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]<p><code>[soliloquy slug="test1"]</code></p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_divider admin_label="Divider" color="#ffffff" show_divider="on" /][et_pb_blurb admin_label="Locally Owned and Operated" title="Locally Owned and Operated" url_new_window="off" animation="top" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center"]</p><p>FixAll Plumbing is locally owned, based and operated. The founders of the company, the staffs and everyone associated with the organization are from the city and surrounding areas of Paramount in California. While there is no standard rule that says locally owned companies are better than those having a nationwide presence or than the franchisees that are often catering to distant areas where they do not have a base, but the reality is that knowledge and awareness helps. When plumbers cater to areas that they are personal extremely familiar with, they are more aware of the challenges that a home, office or commercial property faces. For instance, if you are planning to install a new plumbing system, a local plumbing company would be helpful as they wouldn’t have to find out the building regulations. They would already know. At FixAll Plumbing, we already know the kinds of problems that residents, business owners and property managers face in Paramount and surrounding areas in California. Seldom do we need a briefing from our clients because of the knowledge and albeit due to our expertise.</p><p>[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label="24/7 Emergency Plumbing" title="24/7 Emergency Plumbing" url_new_window="off" animation="top" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center"]</p><p>FixAll Plumbing has designated business hours when you can call us at our office and you can conveniently schedule the plumbing installation, repair, maintenance or replacement but we also have a round the clock emergency service. Whether it is a weekend or a national holiday, at the dead hours of the night or in the wee hours of the morning, if you need the services of a plumbing company on an emergency basis, you would always find us ready to drive out to your place.</p><p>[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label="Satisfaction Guarenteed" title="Satisfaction Guarenteed" url_new_window="off" animation="top" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center"]</p><p>FixAll Plumbing has a unique offering where you are not only happy with the quality of work done but you would also be extremely satisfied with the entire experience. Right from the initial consultation through the schedule to the post service relation that we cherish with our clients, you would be completely satiated with every facet of our service and that is a guarantee.</p><p>[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label="Quality at an Affordable Price" title="Quality at an Affordable Price" url_new_window="off" animation="top" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center"]</p><p>Quality doesn’t come cheap and what comes cheap cannot be of great quality – such is the reality in many cases. With FixAll Plumbing, you experience an exception. We are one of the very few plumbing companies in the state that offers quality work at inexpensive rates.</p><p>[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_sidebar admin_label="Sidebar" orientation="right" area="sidebar-1" background_layout="light" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_testimonial admin_label="Testimonial - Tory" author="Tory - Redondo Beach" url_new_window="off"]</p><p>I have been using Fix-All Plumbing for 5 years now. I have three small children and it seems as though I am always needing a plumber. I have had Fix All Plumbing fix everything from my garbage disposal to toilet issues to hooking up a gas dryer. John is by far the nicest, cleanliest, punctual plumber I have ever met. If he can come the day I call him he will! But Fix All Plumbing goes above and beyond. Today I had company coming in down and a toilet that wasn\'t working. The last thing I needed! I called Fix All Plumbing and they walked me through the issue and I was able to repair it on my own! They totally saved me $$!!!! Thank you so much Fix All Plumbing I really appreciate your professionalism and your willingness to help even at no gain to you.</p><p>[/et_pb_testimonial][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_testimonial admin_label="Testimonial - Don" author="Don - Redondo Beach" url_new_window="off"]</p><p>I had a pipe in a downstairs wall leaking water from an upstairs shower out onto the floor. I called Fix-All Plumbing, and they were very helpful discussing the problem over the phone. John came the next day, located the source of the problem, and fixed it within a few hours. He was also very helpful in describing the issue and the various pipes and construction in the problem area. Thank you for the professional and courteous service!</p><p>[/et_pb_testimonial][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2014-05-14 16:37:25', '2014-05-14 16:37:25', '', 0, 'http://dev1.ken-shoufer.com/fixall//?page_id=50', 0, 'page', '', 0) ; 
