ny coming in down and a toilet that wasn\'t working. The last thing I needed! I called Fix All Plumbing and they walked me through the issue and I was able to repair it on my own! They totally saved me $$!!!! Thank you so much Fix All Plumbing I really appreciate your professionalism and your willingness to help even at no gain to you.</p><p>[/et_pb_testimonial][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_testimonial admin_label="Testimonial - Don" author="Don - Redondo Beach" url_new_window="off"]</p><p>I had a pipe in a downstairs wall leaking water from an upstairs shower out onto the floor. I called Fix-All Plumbing, and they were very helpful discussing the problem over the phone. John came the next day, located the source of the problem, and fixed it within a few hours. He was also very helpful in describing the issue and the various pipes and construction in the problem area. Thank you for the professional and courteous service!</p><p> </p><p>[/et_pb_testimonial][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_text admin_label="Placemarks Map" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]</p><p>[bgmp-map]</p><p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]</p>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-08 01:30:30', '2014-05-08 01:30:30', '', 50, 'http://dev1.ken-shoufer.com/fixall/50-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ; 
