nI had a pipe in a downstairs wall leaking water from an upstairs shower out onto the floor. I called Fix-All Plumbing, and they were very helpful discussing the problem over the phone. John came the next day, located the source of the problem, and fixed it within a few hours. He was also very helpful in describing the issue and the various pipes and construction in the problem area. Thank you for the professional and courteous service!\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_testimonial][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-14 16:35:38', '2014-05-14 16:35:38', '', 50, 'http://dev1.ken-shoufer.com/fixall/50-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ; 
